In scala we can access local files with the help of API scala.io.Source
scala.io.Source
val data = Source("Downloads/names/yob1881.txt").getLines        // .getLines method helps us to get the data as whole line instead of single char

MapReduce using this data :
val dataFilter = data.filter(dataCont => dataCont.split(",")(1).equal("M"))     //boolean values as output of fun and final output is list:Int
val dataMap = dataFilter.map(_.split(",")(2))                                   //one argument and one value output
val dataReduce = dataMap.reduce(_+_)                                           //function with 2 arguments and one value output
